    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro Rally 带你穿越过去的尘土飞扬的道路，无论你是经验丰富的赛车手，还是渴望挑战的新人，都可以沉浸在这个传奇世界中。准备好迎接一场充满速度与激情的旅程，挑战自我，与经典车和强劲对手一较高下！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/f0b475b48e9a991a1da59b8f48340e37.poster.avif?t=1767384662\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/f0b475b48e9a991a1da59b8f48340e37.webm?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/f0b475b48e9a991a1da59b8f48340e37.mp4?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验18辆传奇可驾驶的拉力赛车和14个不同地图带来的拉力激情！每一辆车都将推动你挑战速度和控制的极限，而每个地图则提供独特的挑战和战略机会，让你在每个转弯中都力求卓越。准备好迎接一场充满速度和肾上腺素的旅程吧！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/bacd78a93715890c4a9d898bbf9e06fd.poster.avif?t=1767384662\" width=800 height=800 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/bacd78a93715890c4a9d898bbf9e06fd.webm?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133870/extras/bacd78a93715890c4a9d898bbf9e06fd.mp4?t=1767384662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
